idea:
TeamAspire Venture Pvt Ltd a Navi Mumbai based start-up is here to take care of all the supplies & Services, School needs for education and play, so that school Management, Principal & Teachers can concentrate on the Curriculum & other School Activities & leave the worry of Procurement on us. From interiors, setups, furniture to the smaller requirements like pins. They have it all. All that the school requires can be fetched from Aspire. Parents and guardians can provide their children with good quality school supplies effortlessly by fetching everything under one roof.

Moreover to support the Digital India platform we are in urge to create Websites of almost all the schools in india starting from Maharashtra onwards. Just a small support from us to get all the schools to have their Digital Presence.
name: TEAMASPIRE VENTURES PRIVATE LIMITED

idea:
Anandi Seva Kendra(NGO), located in Nerul, Navi Mumbai. We work in women and child welfare from the past 30 years and have covered various projects affiliated to the Govt of Maharashtra ever since.

We recently started a women empowerment project in the month of september 2020. We introduced an organic and homemade product line consists of the following:

1. Homemade cow ghee

2 . Organic and raw honey (Tulsi, neem, lychee, multiflora, jamun and babul)

3. Organic turmeric

4. Handmade, blended powered spices (Fish curry and chili garlic onion)

The idea was to induce a healthy lifestyle and to empower the women who lost their jobs due to pandemic 2020. We give the needy platform to create a variety of healthy staple products and distribute it to our customers.
name: ASK- Anandi Seva Kendra
